</li>
<li id="cite_note-30"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint"><a href="#cite_ref-30">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text">Tanguy L’Aminot, «&#160;Politique et révolution chez Jean-Jacques Rousseau&#160;», <i>Studies on Voltaire and the Eighteenth Century</i>, <abbr class="abbr" title="volume">vol.</abbr>&#160;324, Voltaire Foundation, 1994.</span>
